snippet.textDisplay:
One of my most favourite songs by Coke Studio. It didn't get as many views though as it should have. But, I believe, people with great taste of music have really appreciated it.

The song has three distinct musical styles beautifully and seamlessly blended in one composition. The central part of song is well suited to the powerful voice of Shilpa Rao.

I think this song will continue to gather respect and appreciation across the world in the coming years from the people who have an ear for music.
